  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency enzyme-adapter-react-15 to v1.2.0",
  "body": "This PR contains the following updates:\n\n| Package | Type | Update | Change | References |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| enzyme-adapter-react-15 | devDependencies | minor | `1.0.5` -> `1.2.0` | [homepage](http://airbnb.io/enzyme/), [source](https://renovatebot.com/gh/airbnb/enzyme) |\n\n---\n\n### Release Notes\n\n<details>\n<summary>airbnb/enzyme</summary>\n\n### [`v1.2.0`](https://renovatebot.com/gh/airbnb/enzyme/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#&#8203;120-December-10-2015)\n\n##### Minor Changes\n\n-   Support for context ([#&#8203;62](https://renovatebot.com/gh/airbnb/enzyme/pull/62))\n\n##### Patches\n\n-   `nodeHasId` fix for some 0.14 corner cases ([#&#8203;65](https://renovatebot.com/gh/airbnb/enzyme/pull/65))\n\n### [`v1.1.0`](https://renovatebot.com/gh/airbnb/enzyme/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#&#8203;110-December-7-2015)\n\n##### Minor Changes\n\n-   Support for Stateless Functional Components ([#&#8203;53](https://renovatebot.com/gh/airbnb/enzyme/pull/53))\n\n##### Patches\n\n-   Tweak `describeWithDOM` messaging ([#&#8203;48](https://renovatebot.com/gh/airbnb/enzyme/pull/48))\n-   Documentation Fixes\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n### Renovate configuration\n\n:date: **Schedule**: \"every weekend\" in timezone Europe/Paris.\n\n:vertical_traffic_light: **Automerge**: Enabled.\n\n:recycle: **Rebasing**: Whenever PR is stale, or if you modify the PR title to begin with \"`rebase!`\".\n\n:no_bell: **Ignore**: Close this PR and you won't be reminded about this update again.\n\n---\n\nThis PR has been generated by [Renovate Bot](https://renovatebot.com/gh/marketplace/renovate). View repository job log [here](https://renovatebot.com/dashboard#algolia/instantsearch.js).",
